name: Beauty In The Simulation
description:
This is my first NFT that I have minted on the Tezos Blockchain, starting off my series of drops. 

Edition 1 of 1 - Oct 2 2021  

Our daily routine makes it seem like we are living a real life RPG. This version of the game needs to patched over, I can’t seem to find the beauty in the simulation. I’m too busy grinding for the next ‘level up’ or ‘achievement’ but I just want to stand still or maybe log off. I guess the game never makes sense.  

More to come. 

1/100

- Yolanda 🍒
